The paper discusses the implementation of recommendation algorithms in a large-scale biomedical knowledge base, which involves processing and analyzing large amounts of data. This suggests that the paper may belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Data Mining (cs.DL), Database (cs.DB), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories of arXiv CS. However, since the focus is on recommendation algorithms, Information Retrieval and Data Mining are the most likely sub-categories.
